	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idMaisie) then

	end
	
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, sLevelAreaName)

-- Music Manager for entering Solitude

	if sLevelAreaName == "Scos_Hills_Solitude" then
		if bClearMusic then
			Hydra.ClearMusicOverride("Sanctuary_Eastern_Continent")
			Hydra.MusicOverride("Sanctuary_Eastern_Continent", "Music_Scosglen_Airidah_Approach3")
			bClearMusic = false
		end
	end

end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

	--TEMP Kill Airidah
	Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(ID_AIRIDAH_WOUNDED)
	Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(ID_AIRIDAH_WOUNDED, false)
	Hydra.ActorSetNeverDie(ID_AIRIDAH_WOUNDED, false)
	Hydra.QActorPower(ID_AIRIDAH_WOUNDED, S_POWER_DEATH)
	
	------------------------------------------------------
	-- Deferred Rewards
	idFirstTimeRewardLocation = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(sFirstTimeRewardDropActor, idActorNPC)
	
	-- Since this boss doesn't have its own treasure class, also drop generic treasure at this time
	Hydra.TreasureClassDropAtActor(idFirstTimeRewardLocation, "Campaign_Mini_Boss")
	
	-- Remove the Reward Actor
	Hydra.ActorDelete(idFirstTimeRewardLocation)
	------------------------------------------------------
	
	Hydra.ActorSetIdleAnim(ID_AIRIDAH_WOUNDED, S_POWER_DIE_LOOP)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(ID_AIRIDAH_WOUNDED) then
		Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(ID_AIRIDAH_WOUNDED, 2.5)
	end
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(ID_AIRIDAH_WOUNDED)
end

function Start(idActor, snoQuest)
	--Switch to non-hostile wounded Airidah
	Hydra.ActorEnable(ID_AIRIDAH_WOUNDED)
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtTarget(ID_AIRIDAH_WOUNDED, ID_AIRIDAH_WOUNDED, S_POWER_FADEIN)
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(ID_AIRIDAH_WOUNDED, 3)
	idVFX = Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(ID_AIRIDAH_WOUNDED, EFF_AIRIDAH_TELEPORT_BURST)
	Hydra.ActorSetAnimSetOverride(ID_AIRIDAH_WOUNDED, ANI_AIRIDAH_WOUNDED)
	Hydra.ActorSetIdleAnim(ID_AIRIDAH_WOUNDED, S_POWER_WOUNDED)

	bBossFight = false
end
